- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also a likely category as the sandpile model has been used to study network dynamics. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the dynamics of a specific algorithmic model. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with the fixed point dynamics of a game-like model. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a possible category as the paper may involve numerical simulations or analysis of the sandpile model.
